### MA40238 Number Theory
My apologies...

The public access to the webpage for MA40238 (Number Theory, 2014/15) has been temporarily disabled, due to this unit being taught again at the University of Bath this semester.

If you would like to access the webpage and the material I used while I taught this course during the first semester of 2014/15, please [contact me](mailto:zhangzy@math.uni-hannover.de).

The full webpage will be online again after the end of the current semester (hopefully in the beginning of 2017).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
